<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Dynamic Select Box - State Names</title>
  <style>
    #stateSelect{
        
    background-color: transparent;
    color: white;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    padding: 4px 3px;
    margin: 6px 0px;
    outline: none;
    border: none;

    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <select id="stateSelect">
        <option value="0">Select a state</option>
      </select>

  <script>
  var e = document.getElementById("stateSelect");

  function onChange() {
      var value = e.value;
      var text = e.options[e.selectedIndex].text;
  
       localStorage.setItem("state",text)
  }
  e.onchange = onChange;
  onChange();
  
  
  const stateSelect = document.getElementById('stateSelect');
  
  function GET(uri, onLoad, onError) {
      // Send the request
      fetch(uri)
          .then(response => {
              if (response.ok) {
                  // Request successful, process the response
                  return response.json();
              } else {
                  // Request failed
                  throw new Error('Error: ' + response.status);
              }
          })
          .then(data => {
              // Do something with the response data
              console.log(data);
              onLoad(data);
              console.log(data);
  
          })
          .catch(error => {
              console.log('Network error', error);
  
              onError();
          });
  }
  
  function retrieveCachedData(dataKey) {
      try {
          const serializedData = localStorage.getItem(dataKey);
          if (serializedData === null) {
              console.log('No cached data found.');
              return null;
          }
          const data = JSON.parse(serializedData);
          console.log('Cached data retrieved successfully!');
          return data;
      } catch (error) {
          console.error('Error retrieving cached data:', error);
          return null;
      }
  }
  
  function SilentLogin() {
      let allStates = retrieveCachedData("States");
      if (!allStates ) {
          console.log("States are not cached something went wrong with the Silent Login!!")
      }

        let states = retrieveCachedData("NotAllowedStates");
        const filteredStates = allStates.filter(s => !states.includes(s));

      filteredStates .forEach(state => {
          const option = document.createElement('option');
  
          option.text = state;
          stateSelect.appendChild(option);
      });
  }
  
  SilentLogin();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
